{"tid":11860,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[煩惱]樓下間茶餐廳好西 試唔試新個間好？","createTime":"2016-11-29T12:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T15:10:42.000Z","uid":16468,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97210843b25efb3c6abb1165bb5ca8df9f5fc966","tid":11860,"uid":16468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:20:14.000Z","msg":"話說樓下間茶餐廳已經開咗十幾年<br />\n都轉過幾次手 依家個老細就幾年前頂手嘅<br />\n裝修舊出餐慢唔再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見過有客食食下飯冇啦啦俾佢趕走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一話佢間鋪d衰野就俾人趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係呢 間茶餐廳就好撚多蝗蟲嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一路食一路噴到d口水週圍都係啦 甚至係到r腳都唔趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係見到都冇胃口<br />\n仲有班人一路食一路大大聲話d牛肉好好味呀 d雞肉好好味呀 但係又唔撚趕佢地走架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n獨市生意冇得唔幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 附近其他餐廳好撚難食<br />\n<br />\n最近好似有人睇唔過眼 係佢隔離新開咗間茶餐廳<br />\n裝修靚出餐快兼好撚好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd食客又正正常常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個老細又和善親民 仲會同d客吹下水添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過依家舊個間個老細係到叫春 話咩「許多假貨，造得比真品還好、更平。」呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一時又話百花齊放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一時又話新果間𠝹走佢d客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以突然間良心好過意唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以想問下LiHKG仔意見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過檔食新野 咪撚理個老細<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 將就下食舊餐廳<br />\n<br />\np.s 新果間個老細之前好似做過批發 將舊果間d野食拎出去賣 不過唔知點解翻咗面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7406659bf90b26c23dc042413322eecc19403e19","tid":11860,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:22:08.000Z","msg":"曲到圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb09957c7faca97c26c49643fed65dce64b1e2e","tid":11860,"uid":16468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:22:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曲到圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為咗小弟個胃著想 俾下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f740a2877f8e83b99159b3bfb7a5000026661a5","tid":11860,"uid":17684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:22:45.000Z","msg":"自已煮麵食好過喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d24d4e39800a908780a81d48adf0d3fa1b1967","tid":11860,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:24:15.000Z","msg":"po去高登會點"},{"pid":"dd82bcc1569356f703e85e3184b0cbad5fd00961","tid":11860,"uid":16468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:24:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自已煮麵食好過喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無飯家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742a8f1a93d1f6f3d16a4fe5f3c4073e6e3f63f8","tid":11860,"uid":16468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>po去高登會點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵人幫手問下高登仔意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc02964cc4351471ed1f145bc3ecdfa9a00a93f","tid":1